00:05:36.720 --> 00:05:37.720
She's not Wu Yang.

00:05:37.750 --> 00:05:38.350
She's not.

00:05:38.720 --> 00:05:40.320
Then that day, why did you...

00:05:40.690 --> 00:05:41.070
I...

