the Fairy Beauty Powder?

00:07:40.920 --> 00:07:42.120
It's been restocked.

00:07:42.800 --> 00:07:44.159
Why not come in and check it out?

00:07:44.159 --> 00:07:44.600
Okay.

00:07:45.000 --> 00:07:45.680
Let's go.

